text: Sebastian Ingrosso (born Sebastian Carmine Ingrosso on 20 April 1983) is a Swedish DJ, producer, and remixer. He is a member of the house music group Swedish House Mafia, alongside Axwell, Eric Prydz, and Steve Angello. His production is mainly classified as electro house and progressive house.
